reviewText: How could anything about this show be less than 5 stars.  A joy and honor to watch a hero.

Excellent, when will season 6 be available

Thank you. Good product, great service.
I love this show. I admire the hard work and true dedication this family has!

This series is very life affirming.  It doesn't matter if I've seen them before.  They still lift my spirits every time, every DVD.
